<div class="com-share" data-id="16401" data-title="《住得起柏悦酒店的那些人，成了《纽约时报》追逐的用户》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16401/medium/16401.jpg?1445411958" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16401.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
